`nx` is a tool suite to manage code repository and documentation.

Configure the tool:

	$ nx config set neo.url http://localhost:7474

Add some repos:

	$ nx repo add std lib/standard
	$ nx repo add lib lib/
	$ nx repo add nit src/

 Push repo to neo:

	$ nx start
	$ nx neo push std

Generate documentation from neo:

	$ nx doc std -d std_doc/

